24561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:35:34.000Z","msg":"可唔可以放塊硬物入個枕頭套到?<br />\n塊硬物可以挺起成個防具，方便穿戴<br />\n個枕頭就用嚟減少衝擊力<br />\n好似避彈衣咁<br />\n除咗本身嘅強化纖維<br />\n仲可以係入面加陶瓷板增加防護力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:38:52.000Z","msg":"著完會跑唔郁"},{"pid":"30d922db9fca1f671cb58fa93468f53ed342fbf0","tid":1374370,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:44:37.000Z","msg":"濕咗水應該就燒唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身可以用繩捆好，捆到好細帶出街！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9b8e42db9d110e19b817c3f7abcfcae1fc56d3","tid":1374370,"uid":94441,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:55:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EDeDCkWYj6E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEDeDCkWYj6E&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F14PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=66490dbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EDeDCkWYj6E</a><br />\n<br />\n平時許多常見的液體都是非牛頓流體，包括水、血液、融化的瀝青或塑膠等。所謂牛頓流體指的是受力時，產生的剪力，也就是液體之中阻撓橫向移動的力量，與受到的力量成正比；而剪切增稠流體，顧名思義，這種液體，在受力的時候，會使得液體結構改變，讓黏度、硬度上升、剪力不成比例的增加，同時也會伴隨體積膨脹，因此也叫「脹流性」液體。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnet.com/news/liquid-body-armor-could-save-you-from-a-bullet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnet.com%2Fnews%2Fliquid-body-armor-could-save-you-from-a-bullet%2F&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F14PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=f3c36c0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnet.com/news/liquid-body-armor-could-save-you-from-a-bullet/</a><br />\n<br />\n當然，愈稠愈好。<br />\n<br />\n至於應用方面可能係鷹粟粉醬灌入吹氣救生衣。"},{"pid":"ffa75697579193e27203ff25790528a401bf4785","tid":1374370,"uid":248619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c9b8e42db9d110e19b817c3f7abcfcae1fc56d3","tid":1374370,"uid":94441,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:55:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EDeDCkWYj6E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEDeDCkWYj6E&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F14PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=66490dbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EDeDCkWYj6E</a><br />\n<br />\n平時許多常見的液體都是非牛頓流體，包括水、血液、融化的瀝青或塑膠等。所謂牛頓流體指的是受力時，產生的剪力，也就是液體之中阻撓橫向移動的力量，與受到的力量成正比；而剪切增稠流體，顧名思義，這種液體，在受力的時候，會使得液體結構改變，讓黏度、硬度上升、剪力不成比例的增加，同時也會伴隨體積膨脹，因此也叫「脹流性」液體。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnet.com/news/liquid-body-armor-could-save-you-from-a-bullet/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnet.com%2Fnews%2Fliquid-body-armor-could-save-you-from-a-bullet%2F&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F14PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=f3c36c0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnet.com/news/liquid-body-armor-could-save-you-from-a-bullet/</a><br />\n<br />\n當然，愈稠愈好。<br />\n<br />\n至於應用方面可能係鷹粟粉醬灌入吹氣救生衣。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:04:27.000Z","msg":"好撚正...好波！"}]}